data.description: Nestled within Southern Highlands, this home offers a serene location on a quiet cul-de-sac. With a spacious design, the home has three bedrooms and a versatile loft. Upon entering the main floor, there is a formal living room that sets the tone for elegant gatherings. The adjacent family room is adorned with built-in illuminated bookshelves and a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The kitchen, featuring an island and sleek granite countertops, is a culinary haven that's both stylish and functional. Each bedroom has custom closets, ensuring ample storage and organization. The bathrooms are appointed with marble countertops, adding a touch of luxury to everyday routines. For outdoor enthusiasts, a covered patio awaits. This home is located in close proximity to great schools and parks. This Southern Highlands gem offers both comfort and functionality for the discerning homeowner.
